properties.name: sleep
properties.description:
The number of milliseconds to wait before adding the next participant.
If it is an array, a random sleep time between the sleep[0] and sleep[1] values will be added
(the difference must be >=100 ms, otherwise, a random sleep time between sleep[1] and sleep[1] + 100
will be added). If sleep is a number, a sleep time equal to its value will be added

otherwise the inviteV4 won't be sent

properties.name: sleep
properties.description: The number of milliseconds to wait before performing an operation for the next requester. If it is an array, a random sleep time between the sleep[0] and sleep[1] values will be added (the difference must be >=100 ms, otherwise, a random sleep time between sleep[1] and sleep[1] + 100 will be added). If sleep is a number, a sleep time equal to its value will be added. By default, sleep is an array with a value of [250, 500]
